<th colspan="2" class="above" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold; color: black; background-color: #dddddd;">Sumerian</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-weight: bold; color: black; background-color: #dddddd;"><span lang="sux" xml:lang="sux">eme-ƒùir, eme-gi</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Spoken natively in</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="Sumer" title="Sumer">Sumer</a> and <a href="Akkadian_Empire" title="Akkadian Empire">Akkad</a></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Region</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="Iraq" title="Iraq">Iraq</a> (<i><a href="Mesopotamia" title="Mesopotamia">Mesopotamia</a></i>)</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Era</th>
<td class="" style="">Attested from 3300 BC. Effectively extinct from about 1800 BC; used as classical language until about 100 AD.</td>
</tr>
