<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Sumerian 26th c Adab.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/91/Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg/300px-Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg" width="300" height="311" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/91/Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg/450px-Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/91/Sumerian_26th_c_Adab.jpg 2x" /></a>
