<tr>
<td style="width:1px;"></td>
<td class="mbox-text plainlist" style="vertical-align:middle; font-size:95%;"><b>This article contains <a href="Help_Special_characters" title="Help:Special characters">special characters</a>.</b> Without proper <a href="Help_Special_characters" title="Help:Special characters">rendering support</a>, you may see <a href="Mojibake" title="Mojibake">question marks, boxes, or other symbols</a>.</td>
